      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>結局、ヴァルハラの魔術の暴走って
魔科学兵器のせいだったんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who would have thought in reality it was a Magitech weapon what caused the Mana to go out of control?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41392</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>１５０年も前のものが
今の時代にも残ってたなんて……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's amazing it was intact for 150 years until the present...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41508</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな危険なものの上で、
みんな何も知らずに生活してたんだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Despite being such a dangerous object no one knew it was there all this time...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もし&lt;Mel&gt;が発見しなかったら、
ずっとあのままだったんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sure if &lt;Mel&gt; hadn't discovered it someone else would, eventually.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41732</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>発見っていうか……
わたしが原因で事故になったっていうか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Discovered it? More like bumping into it by a horrible accident...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41856</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だって、あれからヴァルハラで
調査したら地面からたくさん出てきたんだぜ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sure if we made a thorough research of Valhalla's landscape I'm sure we'd find a lot of undiscovered stuff.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41948</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうだね、それって
&lt;Mel&gt;のおかげだよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't that so? I think it's good &lt;Mel&gt; found it, then.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42032</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか……
……そうなのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really...? I guess that's sort of true...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42124</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_003_084_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほんと、&lt;Mel&gt;って
前向きになんねーのな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Man, nothing convinces this girl to move on.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
